triples.evidence: In ultrasound imaging, we use a device called a transducer, which contains piezoelectric materials. These materials can generate high-frequency sound waves when subjected to an electric current.

evidence: The reflected waves are detected by the transducer, and from this data, we can reconstruct an image of the internal structures.
